<section class="projects" id="projects">
      <h2 class="projects-title">Some of my Recent Projects</h2>
      <div class="projects-container">
        <div class="project-container project-card">
          <img
            src="assets/images/mentalhealth.png"
            alt="expense-tracker"
            loading="lazy"
            class="project-pic"
          />
          <h3 class="project-title">Mental Health Mobile Game</h3>
      <p class="project-details">
        As the Mental Health Mobile Game Research Lead and Software Developer, I collaborated to create a mobile game designed to empower Native Americans, particularly Hopi tribe members, facing mental health challenges. Through manual conversion of Figma wireframes to the dynamic Flutter app development platform, I ensured the game's accessibility across devices. By researching into the intricacies of Hopi culture, I worked to bridge the gap, addressing mental health disparities and nurturing individual resilience.
      </p>
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1QyqpANg_QWqdDRm-dHfDPD_ueayp2md2?usp=sharing" target="_blank" class="project-link">Check it Out</a>
    </div>
    <div class="project-container project-card">
      <img
        src="assets/images/sparsity.png"
        alt="greeny-earth"
        loading="lazy"
        class="project-pic"
      />
      <h3 class="project-title">Sparsity Research</h3>
      <p class="project-details">
        Embarking on an exploration of numerical linear algebra, I undertook the creation of an LU decomposition code from scratch in MATLAB. This initial endeavor paved the way for a deeper exploration into the realm of sparsity optimization. Building upon this foundation, I engineered a bespoke implementation of LU decomposition that harnessed the intrinsic power of sparsity. This journey not only honed my coding prowess but also illuminated the intersection of algorithms and practical mathematics.
      </p>
      <a href="https://vvishal.notion.site/Sparsity-553f4e71c04a4b6dbef191d9f6c4c437?pvs=4" target="_blank" class="project-link">Check it Out</a>
    </div>
